race.comment: Hard to go past CARPACCIO (3). Was simply outclassed in a rich race on Magic Millions day on the Gold Coast but the start prior was placed at Eagle Farm in a BM70. Wins this on that form. BLACK MINTO (6) was placed in the same race. Hit the line well for a close-up third and continued a string of placings, finishing in the money all five since a win six back. PARIAH ENGAGEMENT (11) has been building to a win with placings in the last two and looks one of the major chances.  SUKHBIR (4) drew the outside and went back to last but found the line nicely fresh in a BM70 and wasn't far away. Better draw and fitter again. Goes very well here and right in this.
